  "body": "It would be handy for testing to initialize some of the constants via constructor. \r\nNow I need to modify constants and recompile contract for my testing environment. \r\nIf add constructor params one could use the same binary. \r\nI would like to see the following constants in the constructor: \r\n```\r\nCHAIN_START_FULL_DEPOSIT_THRESHOLD: constant(uint256) = 16384  # 2**14\r\nSECONDS_PER_DAY: constant(uint256) = 86400\r\n```\r\n(the second constant might need to be renamed imho in this case)",
